sequenceDiagram
  participant U as user goals
  participant C as Context
  participant M as Model
  participant H as Harness
  participant T as ToolRuntime
  participant V as Verification

  U->>C: Project current target and evidence
  C->>M: Build model input
  M-->>H: Determine and propose tool intent
  H->>H: validate + permission
  H->>T: Execution tool
  T-->>H: Return original result
  H->>C: projection observation
  C->>M: Next round of input
  H->>V: Run verification
  V-->>H: Is the goal established?
